<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n12128k"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n12" href="#n12128k">N12 (VI.B.14)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n12all.htm#n12128k"> 128(k)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> <font face="wake">H</font>&apos;s hat hung up</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">Beno&icirc;t XIII en ces tristes circonstances e&ucirc;t bien voulu s&apos;assurer encore le concours de ma&icirc;tre Vincent. Il fit tout pour le retenir. Vincent, para&icirc;t-il, refusa le chapeau de cardinal. <br><font color="green">[In these sad conditions Benedict XIII would have preferred to have the help of master Vincent and he did all he could to retain him. But Vincent, it seems, refused the cardinal&apos;s hat.]</font> <small> Matthieu-Maxime Gorce, <a name="STVF" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#STVF"><cite title="source">Saint Vincent Ferrier</cite></a> (1924) 68</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
